<h2 id=3D"CommunicationTheory-4=EF=B8=8F=E2=83=A3Detection/Demodulation"><s=
trong>4=EF=B8=8F=E2=83=A3 Detection / Demodulation</strong></h2>
<p><strong>Detection:</strong> Extract the <strong>original message signal<=
/strong> from the modulated carrier at the receiver.</p>
<div class=3D"table-wrap">
<table data-table-width=3D"760" data-layout=3D"default" data-local-id=3D"2a=
909eb0-0b32-4c5e-aa8d-9a11f357872e" class=3D"confluenceTable">
