<p>Description</p></th>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>AM</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p><strong>Envelope detector</strong></p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Rectifier + RC filter extracts amplitude variations</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>FM</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p><strong>Frequency discriminator / slope detector / PLL</strong></p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Converts frequency variations to voltage</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>PM</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p><strong>Phase-locked loop (PLL)</strong></p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Recovers original phase-modulated signal</p></td>
</tr>
</tbody>
</table>
</div>
<hr>
