<h3 id=3D"CommunicationTheory-=E2=9C=85Summary.5">=E2=9C=85 <strong>Summary=
</strong></h3>
<ul>
<li>
<p><strong>Multiplexing:</strong> Combines multiple signals over one channe=
l =E2=86=92 <strong>FDM</strong> (frequency), <strong>TDM</strong> (time)</=
p></li>
<li>
<p><strong>Multiple Access:</strong> Allows multiple users to share medium =
=E2=86=92 <strong>FDMA, TDMA, CDMA</strong></p></li>
<li>
<p><strong>Applications:</strong> Telecommunication, mobile networks, broad=
casting</p></li>
</ul>
